freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: 10 mins after shot, I became dizzy, diaphoretic, blurred vision and a sudden headache.  My HR and BP were increased.
I have dysautonomia, beginning last evening and throughout today I have had a higher heart rate, blood pressure and the adrenaline rushes.  I have continued to function within my normal.
